{"id": 1803, "genre": 1000, "title": "你最不想参与的职场活动是哪个？", "description": "总让你尬场的职场活动还有哪些？（题图来自：林小妖）", "record_count": 20391, "comment_count": 53, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170717103630lkU70KM5N6jqbBRV.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-07-24T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 2623, "title": "你最不想参与的职场活动是哪个？", "content": "你最不想参与的职场活动是哪个？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 222303, "content": "年会，尤其要求成员表演节目，年度尬", "image": "img/option/option/20170717103724HjKXqhGBnV1Y7OUa.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 222304, "content": "团建旅行，旅行地很近，不会远过小时候春游目的地", "image": "img/option/option/2017071710423886d12NtBeVia4roH.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 222306, "content": "同事婚礼，如果不是关系要好的话，会觉得自己像人形ktv鼓掌器", "image": "img/option/option/201707171044557WpulCJGigTwAZ0B.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 222307, "content": "联谊会，你的一举一动都可能成为明天办公室茶余饭后的八卦谈资", "image": "img/option/option/20170717104547Pv2ywMs5OIxNmSH9.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 222308, "content": "健身团建，经常成为“健身达人展示，体弱者观摩”的一场秀", "image": "img/option/option/20170717104917G1bdHIhx38v6tqJN.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 222309, "content": "线上团建，主要是网游和在线桌游，有职场关系总是不能玩得尽兴", "image": "img/option/option/201707171047544mfdIqx2cDytWJBi.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 222311, "content": "社区服务/组团公益，往往是半强制性，最后举着很丑的横幅合影", "image": "img/option/option/20170717104945XxpWMz3VvjnTYO97.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 222312, "content": "和上司去职场酒会，虽说属于客户应酬，但总是用私人时间还不算加班", "image": "img/option/option/20170717105013TudKlVBYPEXj7hG0.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 222411, "content": "跟工作无关的爱好培训，摄影烹饪彩绘星座入门，浮皮潦草不如听网课", "image": "img/option/option/20170717163129HESRslXVIOB6yu5A.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 222412, "content": "迎新/辞旧会， 容易陷入刻奇的职场聚会", "image": "img/option/option/20170717163159xfS7IEWqiD31jQZe.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 222413, "content": "组团DIY，木工/皮革/制陶/植树，一次性玩耍连门都没入", "image": "img/option/option/20170717163228fE5ewnBS6zYvuGFL.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}